### Product Service Direct Tests

POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-Auth-User: admin@example.com
X-Auth-Roles: ROLE_ADMIN

{
  "sku": "SKU-IPHONE15",
  "name": "iPhone 15",
  "price": 899.99,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

###

POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/products/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
X-Auth-User: user@example.com
X-Auth-Roles: ROLE_USER

{
  "productId": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Superb battery life!",
  "username": "user@example.com"
}

###

POST http://localhost:8083/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { getProducts { sku name price reviews { comment rating } } }"
}

